OTB: Over The Bars

The DH Productions' crew has dug deep into their archive and sifted through more than a decades worth of footage, pulling out the sickest crash clips they could find. 

You will hear first-hand from the athletes involved as they take you through the details and explain why they push their limits for sake of progression. 

Sit back as East Coast downhill legend Lars Tribus and his friends take you through the all of hardcore action. 

OTB is filled with the broken bikes, bones and blood that have made us famous.

Finally all of the carnage is on one DVD for your twisted enjoyment!

Featured Athletes: Aaron Chase, Cam McCaul, Jeff Lenosky, Josh Bender, Randy Spangler, Wayne Goss, Kyle Ebbett, Dave Smutok, Scott Hart, Andrew Neethling, Cam Zink, Mike Kinrade, Steve Romaniuk and Jim DeChamp.
